<h1>✅ Mentor Session Confirmed</h1>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Your mentor session has been confirmed! Get ready for a productive learning experience.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Mentor:</strong> {{mentorName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Topic:</strong> {{sessionTopic}}</p>
  <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{sessionDateTime}}</p>
  <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
  {{#if sessionPrice}}
  <p><strong>Price:</strong> {{sessionPrice}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

{{#if meetingLink}}
<a href="{{meetingLink}}" class="button">Join Meeting</a>
{{/if}}

<h2>Prepare for Your Session</h2>

<p><strong>Before the meeting:</strong></p>
<ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li>Prepare specific questions or topics you want to discuss</li>
  <li>Review relevant course materials</li>
  <li>Test your audio and video setup</li>
  <li>Have a notebook ready for taking notes</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>During the meeting:</strong></p>
<ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li>Be on time (join 2-3 minutes early)</li>
  <li>Have your camera on if possible</li>
  <li>Take notes of key points and recommendations</li>
  <li>Ask questions and seek clarification</li>
</ul>

<h2>Need to Reschedule?</h2>

<p>If you need to cancel or reschedule this session, please do so at least 24 hours in advance:</p>

<a href="{{manageBookingUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; margin: 10px 0;">Manage Booking →</a>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fffbeb; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e;">
    <strong>⚠️ Cancellation Policy:</strong> Cancellations within 24 hours of the scheduled time may not be eligible for a refund.
  </p>
</div>

<p>We hope you have a great session!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The Sinaesta Team</p>
